import { Flex, Text, Grid } from "@chakra-ui/layout";
import { Input } from "../../components/Input/input";
import React from "react";
export const Login = () => {
  return (
    <Flex alignItems="center" padding="10px 15px" height="100vh">
      <Flex
        w="100%"
        justifyContent="center"
        flexDirection="row"
        alignItems="center"
      >
        <Grid w="100%" paddingRight="100px">
          <Flex>
            <Text
              fontWeight="bold"
              fontSize="md"
              color="black"
              paddingRight="5px"
            >
              Burger
            </Text>
            <Text color="secondary.100">kenzie</Text>
          </Flex>
        </Grid>

        <Input placeholder="e-mail" />
        <Input placeholder="Senha" type="password" />
      </Flex>
    </Flex>
  );
};
